## Tier System Implementation
### Free Tier Limitations
- Earthquake: min 4.5 magnitude, hour/day periods only, 5 results max
- Solar: current conditions only, no forecasts/historical, 3 events max
- Volcano: WARNING level only, no region filtering
- Tsunami: Pacific basin only, 3 results max
- Hurricane: Atlantic basin only, no forecast tracks, 3 results max
- Wildfire: warnings only, no region filtering, 3 results max
- Severe Weather: 24h only, extreme/severe only, 3 results max, no state filtering
- Floods: 24h only, major stage only, 3 results max, no river gauges
- Air Quality: US only, PM2.5/O₃ only, 3 results max
- Threats: terrorism (DHS) only, 3 results max
- Space Weather: 24h only, 5 results max
- Drought: Not available (premium only)

### Premium Tier Features
- Full magnitude ranges, extended time periods, region filtering
- Forecast data, historical data, comprehensive results (25 max)
- All alert levels, all basins, all pollutants
- State filtering, coordinate search, river gauge integration
- Multi-country coverage, all threat types
- Drought monitoring with D0-D4 levels and trend analysis